{"tid":1392974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多三毛叫人騎劫/唔好去公務員集會","createTime":"2019-08-01T02:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:49:01.000Z","uid":243262,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97bcf398b6c2221c1e1bdd7a509cafeefb95e4ad","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"咁代表d乜??<br />\n即係港共政府好撚驚多人去呀!!<br />\n敵人逾驚既野我地就更加要去做!!!<br />\n<br />\n吹到勇武派係on9咁 出親黎都會有衝突<br />\n除左係搞分化外<br />\n無非係想嚇走一班細膽和理非<br />\n減少集會既人數,亦想令集會失焦<br />\n<br />\n今次既集會係一個具指標性既集氣大會<br />\n逾多人去參與支持<br />\n公務員就逾有信心進行下一步行動<br />\n同樣地 廣大市民亦更有決心參與5/8既大罷工<br />\n所以我地每一個人既參與都係好重要!!"},{"pid":"244220a3cc8419178647a12908efb7ce17728502","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd919e41af65522ac6ac80d0a7d404dce7ce2a2","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"188cfe98500cb050d5986eb02bc1aa8a074fad23","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ace33395b1d4a68491530dfd1d29a8ddf39da429","tid":1392974,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"政府原來驚人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9ce3a06fe08a9b2f356b2bab09bdc96b859d31","tid":1392974,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7604f9c7fd84033d2bda4f06dc550e456ea519f","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b5254057c25c79861b0947700ba64d0676b45f2","tid":1392974,"uid":243262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}